slides.title: Controversy Network: Hate speech and Social Media 2015
Core elements
slides.text: The most central elements are newsmedia (e.g. Wired). Academia is a little bit detached on the right. Apparently different categories of actors are very distinguished/separated.

slides.title: High degree nodes
slides.text: Some of the nodes with the highest degree are not necessarily the more connected in the overall network. In this case it is a private company, reaching out for publicity.
